{"word":"G782 - ἀσπάζομαι - aspázomai - as-pad'-zom-ahee - Embrace","slug":"G782","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀσπάζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>aspázomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>as-pad'-zom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Embrace"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C3;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - aspazomai</b> - <i>as-pad'-zom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a particle of union) and a presumed form of <a href=\"#/G4685\">G4685</a>; to <i>enfold</i> in the arms, that is, (by implication) to <i>salute</i>, (figuratively) to <i>welcome:</i> - embrace, greet, salute, take leave."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G783\">G783</a>"}]}